T02TD1673E:199a-1: shr'i badzra he ru ka n'a ma no pi ka / bod skad du /
T02TD1673E:199a-2: dpal he ru ka zhes bya ba'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD1673E:199a-3: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1673E:199a-4: dngos dang dngos med rtog bral zhing //
T02TD1673E:199a-5: thugs rje mdzad pa sna tshogs snang //
T02TD1673E:199a-6: thabs mkhas khro ston rgyal ba'i sku ;
T02TD1673E:199a-9: de nyid sgrub thabs cho gar bcas //
T02TD1673E:199a-11: cung zad 'jug pa'i don phyir bshad //
T02TD1673E:199a-12: theg mchog bla ma bzang las byung //
T02TD1673E:199a-13: yon tan stobs sogs kun nas mdzes //
T02TD1673E:199a-14: rab tu sbyangs pa'i rnal 'byor mchog /'dod pa'i lha la dad mos 'dud //
T02TD1673E:199a-15: tshul khrims brtul zhugs la sogs kyi //
T02TD1673E:199a-16: thabs mkhas yan lag rnam spyad pas //
T02TD1673E:199a-17: de nas goms byed las rdzogs te //
T02TD1673E:199b-0: byams sogs @199b tshad med bzhi rnams kyis //
T02TD1673E:199b-1: 'gro rnams thams cad nye bar gzung //
T02TD1673E:199b-2: shin tu dag pa'i gnas nyid du //
T02TD1673E:199b-3: bde ba'i stan la legs par gnas //
T02TD1673E:199b-4: yang dag dkyil 'khor bzang po nyid //
T02TD1673E:199b-5: yang dag khrus kyi cho ga dang //
T02TD1673E:199b-6: yang dag mchod rgyan gtor mar bcas //
T02TD1673E:199b-7: yang dag phyag rgya sngags sogs ldan //
T02TD1673E:199b-8: thams cad yul kun rnam dag pa'i //
T02TD1673E:199b-9: byang chub sems nyid brtan pa las //
T02TD1673E:199b-10: thugs rjes nyi ma'i mtha' yas zer //
T02TD1673E:199b-11: thams cad yul kun khyab par gsal //
T02TD1673E:199b-13: srung ba'i 'khor lo rgya chen po //
T02TD1673E:199b-15: khro tshogs sprul bcas tshom rngam tshogs //
T02TD1673E:199b-16: phyogs bcur bstan par bya ba'i phyir //
T02TD1673E:199b-17: h'um bzhi'i phyag rgya sngags kyis bsrung //
T02TD1673E:199b-18: rigs kyi yi ge mtshan mar bcas //
T02TD1673E:199b-20: sangs rgyas thams cad bsdu byas te//
T02TD1673E:199b-21: gtum rngam khros pa'i cha lugs can //
T02TD1673E:199b-22: thams cad gcig tu sbyor ba'i mthus //
T02TD1673E:199b-23: dam tshig rgyal po he ru ka //
T02TD1673E:199b-24: zhal gcig phyag gnyis mthing ga'i mdangs //
T02TD1673E:199b-26: khro rtags mtshan ma kun rdzogs shing //
T02TD1673E:199b-27: nyams dgu'i rngam brjid tshul dang bcas //
T02TD1673E:199b-28: spyan dmar mche gtsigs khro gnyer can //
T02TD1673E:199b-29: g-yas pa rdo rje rtse lnga gdengs //
T02TD1673E:199b-30: g-yon pa snod bcud kha tv'am bcas //
T02TD1673E:199b-31: klu rgyal brgyad kyis nyer mdzes shing //
T02TD1673E:199b-33: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor phyogs bcur spro //
T02TD1673E:199b-34: rdo rje phreng ba phyag rgya lnga //
T02TD1673E:199b-35: rigs kyi dbu rgyan sems dpar bcas //
T02TD1673E:199b-36: gnas gsum 'od gsal dag byed pa'i //
T02TD1673E:199b-37: dkyil 'khor la gnas sku gsungs thugs //
T02TD1673E:199b-38: phyogs bcur spro zhing bsdus pa'i mthus //
T02TD1673E:199b-39: byin brlabs gnas gsum brtan bar 'gyur //
T02TD1673E:199b-40: snying ga'i 'od zer rgya chen pos //
T02TD1673E:199b-41: rigs kyi khro bo kun bsdus te //
T02TD1673E:199b-42: rang gi gnas su brtan byas nas //
T02TD1673E:199b-43: 'dod pa'i dngos grub gsol ba gdab //
T02TD1673E:199b-44: phyi nang mchod pa sna tshogs kun //
T02TD1673E:199b-45: rgya chen spro zhing dag par dbul //
T02TD1673E:199b-46: tshad med bzhi yi phyag rgya yis //
T02TD1673E:200a-0: sku gsung thugs su sbyor par @200a * //
T02TD1673E:200a-2: ting 'dzin sems dpa'i mtshan ma la //
T02TD1673E:200a-3: sngags kyi 'khor lo spro zhing bsdu //
T02TD1673E:200a-4: aom shr'i he ru ka h'i sv'a h'a //
T02TD1673E:200a-5: mar me'i phreng ba 'khor ba'i tshul //
T02TD1673E:200a-6: yan lag rdzogs pa'i ting 'dzin gyis //
T02TD1673E:200a-7: dngos grub mtshan ma kun ston cing //
T02TD1673E:200a-8: yang dag byang chub brtan par 'gyur /
T02TD1673E:200a-9: thams cad nam mkha'i mtshan nyid de //
T02TD1673E:200a-10: nam mkha' la yang mtshan nyid med //
T02TD1673E:200a-11: khams gsum dag ni ma lus pa //
T02TD1673E:200a-12: thams cad sgyu ma lta bu ste //
T02TD1673E:200a-13: ji ltar sgyur ma thams cad du //
T02TD1673E:200a-14: mthong ba dag ni reg par 'gyur //
T02TD1673E:200a-15: dmigs su yod pa ma yin te //
T02TD1673E:200a-16: de bzhin 'gro ba kun gyi tshul//
T02TD1673E:200a-17: bud med la sogs rin chen mchog / mkha' las dngos grub thams cad spyod //
T02TD1673E:200a-18: dngos po med par bdag sbyor bas //
T02TD1673E:200a-19: nam mkha' kun dang mnyam par sbyor //
T02TD1673E:200a-20: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde ba'i mchog / shin tu bstan pas 'grub par 'gyur //
T02TD1673E:200a-21: spyod lam kun du ma nyams par //
T02TD1673E:200a-23: rnam pa mang po'i yul can kun //
T02TD1673E:200a-24: thabs dang shes rab rol mo'i tshogs //
T02TD1673E:200a-25: bza' btung dag pa'i ting 'dzin gyis //
T02TD1673E:200a-27: bsod nams ye shes tshogs chen la //
T02TD1673E:200a-28: 'gro rnams dag par nye bar sbyor //
T02TD1673E:200a-29: kun du cha lugs chu zla bzhin //
T02TD1673E:200a-30: ma gos chags pa med pa'i rgyal //
T02TD1673E:200a-31: thams cad chos rnams blang dor med //
T02TD1673E:200a-32: bya ba'i lam rdzogs mthar phyin 'gyur //
T02TD1673E:200a-33: tshe 'dir yon tan chos kun dang //
T02TD1673E:200a-35: thams cad sbyor ba'i rgyud chen po //
T02TD1673E:200a-36: de nyid nges par bstan pa'i don //
T02TD1673E:200a-37: phyag rgya gci pa'i sgrub thams mchog / yang dag rdzogs pa'i tshul gyis 'jug / legs par bsdus pa'i bsod nams kyis //
T02TD1673E:200a-38: khams gsum thams cad bcom ldan 'das //
T02TD1673E:200a-39: stobs mchog dpal ldan he ru kar //
T02TD1673E:200a-40: yang dag nyid du grol gyur cig / dpal he ru ka zhes bya ba'i sgrub thabs slob dpon chen po thu bo ra dza ha stis mdzad pa rdzogs so//
